{"tid":505221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【濃霧中叛逃】再有北韓士兵越過休戰區 逃到南韓變節","createTime":"2017-12-21T01:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T02:23:29.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5d66a785cef126d5fee0039b7620f657f2904cf2","tid":505221,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:19:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171221&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57608311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171221%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57608311&d=Lae4Q969r7wfmezT87%2Byq8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=66fe36a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171221%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57608311&h=9feae00e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171221&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57608311</a>"},{"pid":"6e34d01ce4b45355d1385fc4d47680736bdd0e19","tid":505221,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:20:55.000Z","msg":"再有北韓士兵變節，南韓國防部指，一名北韓士兵周四早上越過南北韓邊境非軍事區（DMZ）投奔南韓。<br />\n<br />\n國防部發言人指，變節的北韓士兵是基層人員，在當地時間周四早上8時04分(本港7時04分)，在濃霧中越過邊境逃到南韓。雙方未開一槍。這是五個星期內，第二宗類似事件。<br />\n11月中一名北韓士兵越過休戰區兩韓邊境投奔南韓，北韓士兵猛烈開火阻止，他身中5槍受重傷，事發後北韓已撤換了板門店共同警備區的所有警備兵力。<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"859d1a3e4ab7774a05bf58d40417e346d2547be5","tid":505221,"uid":125731,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:22:27.000Z","msg":"開槍既反而係自己友？？"},{"pid":"b08b23d38060a0e7ab2a05ba05fe04c6b6f95007","tid":505221,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:23:37.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc69c1b1c0a84ccb657ac0ee30325c1068f5a9c","tid":505221,"uid":470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開槍既反而係自己友？？</blockquote><br />\n睇新聞+用下腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas